Rodent's classes are merely classifications and suggestions on how the rodent should be played. However, some abilites whether passive or activate may target a specific class.

=== Vanguard
Low-cost, expendable Rodents designed for deployment during the early phases of a match. These units are typically weaker.

=== Tank

Defensive Rodents with height, enabling them to provide cover for allied units. These rodents have higher defense and health.

=== Specialist

Unique Rodents with unconventional mechanics or playstyles that defy standard classification. 

=== Support

Utility-focused Rodents that can buff or heal allies. They can also debuff enemies.
 
=== Duelist

Offensive Rodents optimized for high damage output.
